<h3>Brches of Ecology</h3>

<section id="boxes">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="box">
          <img src="population ecology.jpg">
          <h4>POPULATION ECOLOGY </h4>
          <p>Studies the dynamics of a single species population, including factors like density, growth rate, and dispersion. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
          <img src="ecosystem ecology.jpg">
          <h4>ECOSYSTEM ECOLOGY </h4>
          <p>Analyzes the relationships between living organisms and their non-living environment within a specific ecosystem. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
          <img src="community ecology.jpg">
          <h4>COMMUNITY ECOLOGY</h4>
          <p>Examines interactions between different species within a given area, like competition, predation, and mutualism. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
